<div class="w-1/2"><br>I'm designing the material that is going to maximize the energy density 
of the carbon nanotube supercapacitor. Namely, my research is focused on
developing a high-k dielectric using the Atomic Layer Deposition technique.
Furthermore, I'm creating and optimizing the hardware required to power
electric motors with the carbon nanotube supercapacitor.</div>
